data.What are your main health concerns or sy: I've been experiencing chronic fatigue and brain fog for the past year. It's really affecting my work and daily life. I also have digestive issues and joint pain.
data.List any medications or supplements you: Levothyroxine 50mcg daily, Vitamin D3 2000 IU, Magnesium 400mg

data.What are your main health concerns or sy: Weight management has been difficult, and I'm having trouble controlling my blood sugar levels. I also snore heavily and wake up tired.
data.List any medications or supplements you: Metformin 1000mg twice daily, Lisinopril 10mg daily, CPAP machine for sleep

data.Describe your typical daily diet: I try to eat healthy but often skip breakfast due to time constraints. Lunch is usually a salad or sandwich, dinner varies. I notice bloating after most meals, especially those with dairy or gluten.

data.Describe any family history of hormonal: My mother had thyroid issues and my grandmother had diabetes. There's also a history of PCOS on my mother's side.
